Resolve the {@link ScopeMetadata} appropriate to the supplied_bean definition._

Implementations can of course use any strategy they like to_determine the scope metadata, but some implementations that spring_immediately to mind might be to use source level annotations_present on {@link BeanDefinition#getBeanClassName() the class} of the_supplied definition, or to use metadata present in the_{@link BeanDefinition#attributeNames()} of the supplied definition._@param definition the target bean definition_@return the relevant scope metadata_ never null
